/* NBAT -- the next VERGE battle system
 * by Andy
 * May 21,'99-
 *
 * Things done:
 *
 * Programmable enemy AI
 * Psudo-Real Time (kind of like FF on wait mode)
 * Normal attacks
 * Magic
 * Items
 * Running away
 * Entity based
 *
 * New things:
 * Defending (done)
 * Elementals (fire,water,etc...) (done)
